## IObjectType type

Represents a strongly typed object i.e. `\{ name: string, value: 5 \}`

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type IObjectType<T extends IBodyType = IBodyType> = {
    type: 'object';
    definition: T;
    extract?: ITypePropertyType[];
};
```
